'''''The New Jedi Order: Knightfall III: Jedi Blood''''' was the third book in the canceled [[Knightfall Trilogy]] of the [[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order|New Jedi Order series]]. It was to be written by [[Michael Jan Friedman]], with the cover art by [[Terese Nielsen]]. The plot would have dealt with [[Danni Quee]] and [[Jorallen]] fighting a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[High Priestess/Legends|High Priestess]] to stop the Vong from mass-murdering [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].

